Sekolah Berasrama Penuh Integrasi Tun Abdul Razak (English: Tun Abdul Razak Integrated Residential School, abbreviated InSTAR) was one of 67 boarding schools (SBP) in Malaysia. The school is located in Pulau Serai, Pekan, Pahang. In 2009, the boarding school integration Tun Abdul Razak has 197 boys and 228 girls, making a total enrolment of 425 people. It has a total of 58 teachers.
Generality of these school sites is 38 acres located in the state assembly Peramu Jaya, Pekan Parliament, about 15 km from the city town and 35 km from Kuantan.
Beyond Success is the school motto and the vision is Success is Education for Life.
